  schema:name "Jason Beckman" ;
  schema:description "Co-founder and Managing Partner of Colbeck Capital Management, a New York-based hybrid-credit boutique. Former Goldman Sachs (Hybrid Lending Group). Colbeck's $362 million in secured debt at ~24% interest funded Fabian Thylmann's 2010 Manwin/MindGeek acquisition — the financing that bootstrapped the contemporary online-pornography platform consolidation." ;
